name: LieutenAnt-Max
description:
Help Max as he tries to provide for his Queen and Colony. Gather the items they request and see if you can make it to the rank of Lieutenant!

The game was created for ZenoJam - The perfect jam for beginners.

Credits :

Programming: Ivan Varava
Art: Raluca Manaila
Story and Dialogue: Julie Morin
Level Design: Oksana Bykova
